03:29.810 --> 03:36.560
Well you really kind of need another viewport or another window here on the interface so you can see

03:36.560 --> 03:38.020
through the camera.

03:38.030 --> 03:43.470
So what I'm going to do for the time being just to give us some extra screen room without adding no

03:43.790 --> 03:45.270
new window in here.

03:45.320 --> 03:53.060
I'm going to change the outliner view to the camera view since I'm pretty much done with my modeling.

03:53.060 --> 03:55.220
