And another thing you can do to make it a little easier to move the camera around it to change from

04:38.570 --> 04:41.340
global to local transformations.

04:41.600 --> 04:42.840
And that's right down here.

04:42.890 --> 04:52.340
So we can change this from global to local and now you can see that the transform gizmos are inline

04:52.430 --> 04:57.460
with the object so we can move that in now and lift it up.

04:57.470 --> 05:05.090
We can rotate it I'll change to the rotate manipulator and rotate it up a bit.

05:06.250 --> 05:08.750
Now move it down some like this.

05:08.750 --> 05:19.700
We can look at it like that maybe I'll rotate it back like this at something like that so I get a better

05:19.700 --> 05:22.070
view of my scene.

05:23.590 --> 05:26.080
There we go that's not too bad.

