So now that we have that let's go ahead and add a light now as I was moving the camera around I accidentally

05:33.730 --> 05:40.840
clicked and move the cursor so the cursor is over here instead of in the center of the grid wherever

05:40.840 --> 05:45.160
the cursor is is where a new object is going to come into the scene.

05:45.160 --> 05:52.300
So I'm going to move this cursor into the center of the grid with shift s and I'll say cursor to center

05:53.050 --> 05:55.450
and then I'll create a point light.

05:55.870 --> 05:56.570
And then we go.

05:56.570 --> 06:02.190
Now I'm going to move it up and into the scene say right about.

06:02.300 --> 06:02.840
Let's move it.

06:02.840 --> 06:10.030
